## 4 | AUTONOMOUS HEALTHCARE COMMAND CENTER

Commander’s Intent → Five ADCs → Continuous S‑R‑D‑A‑L loop.

| ADC    | Function           | Example Outcome                |
| ------ | ------------------ | ------------------------------ |
| SENSE  | Prioritize signals | Sepsis flagged 6 h pre‑symptom |
| REASON | Set analysis depth | 5 min full causal work‑up      |
| DECIDE | Choose strategy    | Early antibiotics protocol     |
| ACT    | Coordinate tasks   | Labs, ICU prep, team alerts    |
| LEARN  | Update models      | Detection algorithm refined    |

